  "title": "TikTok/IG Content creator",
  "description": "<h2>📱 Job Title: TikTok / Instagram Content Creator</h2><h3>📍 Role Overview</h3><p>We’re looking for a <strong>creative, trend-savvy Content Creator</strong> to produce engaging short-form videos for TikTok and Instagram. You’ll be responsible for ideating, filming, editing, and posting content that aligns with our brand voice while staying on top of current social media trends.</p><h3>🎯 Key Responsibilities</h3><ul><li><p>Create engaging <strong>short-form video content</strong> for TikTok & Instagram Reels</p></li><li><p>Brainstorm and execute <strong>content ideas, trends, and hooks</strong></p></li><li><p>Film and edit videos using mobile apps (e.g. CapCut, InShot, native IG/TikTok tools)</p></li><li><p>Write captions, on-screen text, and basic CTAs</p></li><li><p>Stay updated with <strong>viral trends, sounds, and formats</strong></p></li><li><p>Maintain consistent posting schedule</p></li><li><p>Collaborate with the marketing/team to align content with campaigns</p></li><li><p>Track performance (views, engagement) and suggest improvements</p></li></ul>",
